snippet.title: Survivania - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Play FREE on Moonspod.itch.io! - https://moonspod.itch.io/survivania

Survivania is a 2D Score Attack game where you fight hoards of the Demon Lords minions until you inevitebly meet your end.

Keep your Combo high, Score high!

Playable in browser (your score and settings will not be saved, it is recomended to download the game)

Now go, Face Thy Foes! - https://moonspod.itch.io/survivania
More from me - https://www.moonspod.com
Twitter - https://twitter.com/MoonsPod
